🎨 UI/UX Design Prompt (GitHub Profile World)

Prompt:

Design a modern, visually stunning web UI/UX for a product called “GitHub Profile World.”

This app transforms a developer’s GitHub profile into an interactive visual world.
The design should feel futuristic, developer-focused, and highly shareable on social media.

Style & Mood

Futuristic developer aesthetic

Clean, minimal but visually powerful

Dark theme primary (with neon accents)

Inspired by: Stripe, Linear, Vercel, GitHub, and modern SaaS landing pages

Slight cyberpunk + 3D feel

Glassmorphism and soft glow effects

Smooth micro-animations and transitions

Layout Sections

1. Hero Section

Large headline: “Turn your GitHub into a living world”

Subtext explaining visualization of repos, commits, and activity

Input field to enter GitHub username

CTA button: “Generate My World”

Background: animated 3D world or floating code elements

2. Live Preview Section

Mock visualization of a GitHub world

Repos as buildings

Stars as glowing particles

Commits as trees or paths

Activity heatmap as terrain

Floating UI cards showing stats

3. Features Section

GitHub data visualization

Real-time updates

Shareable public link

Developer portfolio enhancement

Custom themes

Use modern card-based layout with icons.

4. How It Works

Enter username

Generate world

Explore and share

Simple 3-step horizontal layout.

5. Developer Credibility Section

Built for developers

Works with public GitHub profiles

Privacy safe

Fast generation

6. Footer

Minimal, modern

Links to GitHub repo, demo, and creator

UI Requirements

Fully responsive (desktop first, then mobile)

Smooth hover states

Rounded corners

Modern typography (Inter, Geist, or similar)

Soft shadows and depth

Dark background with gradient highlights

Subtle animations

Technical context (important)

Frontend will be built with:

Next.js

Tailwind

Framer Motion

Possibly Three.js for 3D world

Design must be developer-friendly and realistic to implement.

Output needed

Provide:

Landing page layout

Component structure

UI hierarchy

Color palette

Typography suggestions

Interaction ideas

Make it look like a premium startup product that could go viral among developers.